data.description: A VA loan "assumption" is when a borrower takes over an existing mortgage, and it's possible even if the buyer isn't a military service member, veteran or eligible surviving spouse. This type of transaction can benefit both homebuyers and sellersWelcome home! This single-story, 3-bed, 2-bath.Tucked away in the sought-after neighborhood of Southern Hills in East San Antonio, in a gated community. This residence emanates timeless chic with stunning finishes and impeccable details. Soak up the curb appeal of the brick and stone exterior as the manicured front gardens welcome you. Step inside, and the wide-open layout rushes to greet you- But that's not all-Southern Hills includes walking trails, a playground, and a covered pavilion for community residents. Its fabulous East San Antonio location means proximity to Brooks Park, Calaveras Lake Park, main roads, retail and walk to Sinclair Elementary and 15 minute commute to Ft Sam Houston/Brooke Army Medical Center. Look no further-everything you seek is right here! Welcome HOME
